Package: RegCompassR
Title: Multiome-Supported Reaction Capacity and GRN Meta-Module Analysis
Version: 1.4.3
Authors@R: c(person(given = "RegCompass", family = "Developers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dev@example.com"))
Description: Runs a strict-stratum RNA+ATAC metacell workflow with signed Pando regulatory evidence, conservative GPR aggregation, zero-preserving absolute reaction evidence, local and global FASTCORE completion, one shared GEM, sample-by-cell-type inference, and directional minimum evidence-discordance scoring.
